                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2620" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-0571</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9242 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">水土不服？——沃尔玛企业文化该如何落地生根？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Acclimatized? — Wal-Mart&#39;s corporate culture how to put down roots </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王宁，刘海园</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">美国沃尔玛百货公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化；跨文化管理；本土化；绩效激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">corporate culture; cross-cultural management; localization; performance incentive</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了沃尔玛公司企业文化在中国充分本土化过程中遇到的障碍，并针对公司在中国市场遭遇的经营困局，讨论分析困局产生的原因。沃尔玛公司“尊重个人、服务顾客、追求卓越”的企业文化为其成功起到了巨大作用，但纵观沃尔玛公司在中国市场的业绩表现、时常曝出的负面新闻，使其企业文化中“诚信”、“尊重个人”等受到严峻的考验和质疑。公司过度追求销售业绩与利润业绩的增长，并没有在中国市场得到回报，反而市场份额有继续被蚕食的倾向。本案例分析了沃尔玛公司在中国遭遇经营困局的成因并给出了破局尝试，使学生充分探究类似沃尔玛公司这样的大型跨国公司应如何塑造既符合本公司文化又有足够适应性的本土企业文化。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the obstacles encountered by Wal-Mart&#39;s corporate culture in China full localization process, and discusses the reasons why the obstacles generate. Wal-Mart&#39;s &quot;respect for the individual, customer service, the pursuit of excellence&quot; corporate culture plays a significant role in its success, but look at Wal-Mart&#39;s performance in the Chinese market, negative news are often exposed, which makesthecorporate culture of &quot;integrity&quot; and &quot;respect for the individual&quot; have been sorely tested and questioned. The excessive pursuit of sales growth and profit performance didn’t pay off in the Chinese market, but its market has a tendency to continue to be eroded. This case study the causes of Wal-Mart experience operating dilemma in China and gives the breaking attempts, so that students can fully explore how a large international company like Wal-Mart shapes its local corporate culture which is not only in line with the company&#39;s culture but also has enough adaptability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业文化》、《企业跨文化管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业文化、企业跨文化管理、战略管理、人力资源管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017-03</td>
                            </tr>
